## <a id="breaking-changes"></a> Breaking Changes in Scheduler v1.4.0

Scheduler v1.4.0 includes the following breaking change:

### <a id='metadata-path'></a> Metadata path within product has changed

The path to the tile metadata within the product has changed from `metadata/p_scheduler.yml`
to `metadata/metadata.yml`. This is an internal implementation detail, however if you
have built automation that relies on the previous path of the metadata within the tile
it will need to be updated.

This change should not affect most users of the scheduler.

